description:
This is a 22 minute workout called '20 MIN FULL BODY TONING & STRENGTH (Total Body Workout At Home)' from the channel MadFit.
The workout falls under Strength/Weight workout and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Weights for this workout.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Foundation Builder vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Follow along with this 20 minute total body TONING AND STRENGTHENING workout AT HOME ! We are using a set of DUMBBELLS for this workout, but you can use anything you have available to you at home. Targets legs, booty, shoulders, arms, and back!
